****** ** ** ********* ******* *** makes her patients feel warm and welcome. She takes time to explain the problems and provides accurate advice. She is also very patient and spends time to understand your concerns and provides suitable remedies. I would highly recommend her for any dental concerns, she’s the first dentist that has made me feel very comfortable and allayed my general fears about going to a dentist, thank you Bijina!

Also, the support staff make sure that the clinic as a whole is neat and clean. Not to forget, the lab services are fantastic!
